    "description": "The rubber duck is a light, hollow bath toy traditionally made from rubber or plastic. In Jutland it serves as an all-purpose weapons test platform, so aircraft emerging from it are entirely intentional. Its most dangerous feature is a rear-facing railgun that fires a distinctive red projectile.",
