        "value": "Ramming"
      }
    ],
    "description": "The Droplet is an alien probe from Liu Cixin's science-fiction novel The Three-Body Problem. Its perfectly smooth, extremely strong shell reflects electromagnetic radiation and remains near absolute zero. During the Doomsday Battle, a single Droplet destroys most of humanity's space fleet by repeatedly ramming its warships.",
    "author": "Unknown",
    "links": [
      {
        "name": "Wikipedia — Droplet",
        "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The%20Three-Body%20Problem%20%28novel%29"
      }
    ]
