    "description": "The ocean sunfish, Mola mola, is a large pelagic fish found in temperate and tropical seas worldwide. It is among the heaviest living bony fishes and has a distinctive flattened body that resembles a fish head without a conventional tail. In the game it serves as an unusually durable target.",
