    "description": "Hakuryū is the game's name for an enlarged development of Japan's wartime G-15 carrier design. The concept builds on the armored flight deck and protected aviation facilities of Taihō while expanding the hull and air group. No ship of this design was laid down before Japan's carrier program collapsed.",
