    "description": "Skoryy represents the Soviet Project 30bis destroyers, the first large postwar destroyer series built for the Soviet Navy. The class combined conventional guns, torpedoes, and anti-submarine weapons in a robust design. Seventy ships were completed, forming an important part of Soviet and allied fleets during the early Cold War.",
