      }
    ],
    "description": "Jiujiang was converted into a Chinese naval fire-support ship built around a 1,700-ton frigate hull. Twin 100 mm and 37 mm guns provided conventional surface and air defense, while extensive multiple rocket launchers delivered short, concentrated bombardments. Additional Type 65 anti-submarine rockets supplied close-range forward-firing capability.",
