        "value": "Nonefixed armament"
      }
    ],
    "description": "Peace Ark is the People's Liberation Army Navy's Type 920 hospital ship, commissioned in 2008. Purpose-built for medical support and humanitarian missions, she carries operating rooms, intensive-care facilities, diagnostic equipment, and hundreds of hospital beds. The ship has conducted repeated overseas deployments across Asia, Africa, the Pacific, and Latin America.",
    "author": "Unknown",
    "links": [
